company_info.description: HUMAN MADE Inc. designs and produces apparel and lifestyle products. It offers clothing, shirts, and hats; and lifestyle products, such as interior goods and towels. The company sells its products through e-commerce and store channels. HUMAN MADE Inc. was formerly known as Otsumo Co., Ltd. and changed its name to HUMAN MADE Inc. in May 2024. The company was incorporated in 2016 and is based in Shinagawa, Japan.
